import { Grid, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import { Box, Container } from '@mui/system'
import React from 'react'

const OurStory = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
        <Box mt={8} align="center">
            <Typography variant='h4' p={2} sx={{textTransform: 'uppercase'}}>
                the work of a lifetime
            </Typography>
            <Typography sx={{width: {xs: "90%", sm: "70%", md: "60%"}}} textAlign="justify">
                As an 8 year old boy I would spend my afternoons exploring a small creek near our cabin in Northern Wisconsin.
                I would walk under the canopy of oak trees exploring, seeking, learning and playing on the creek's banks.
                When I founded Stone Creek Coffee as a 24 year old it was that ethos that I wanted to infuse into our new company.
                We continue this work today and welcome you to our coffee family.   
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant='h5' textAlign="center" ml={18} mt={2}>
                - Ted, Founder 
            </Typography>
        </Box>

        <Box mt={15}>
        <Grid container spacing={2} align="center">
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} >
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quam dignissimos laudantium odit! Ipsa, repudiandae sed. Ullam vero voluptate ab libero quos fugiat, ex blanditiis, provident debitis, ipsa amet nisi minus sint aspernatur quia molestiae necessitatibus veritatis dolor cupiditate. Possimus doloremque est nisi quidem perspiciatis, sequi, molestias, ipsum pariatur dolorum voluptate adipisci? Corrupti dignissimos, quos nam ullam earum nostrum quas laborum nesciunt sit itaque eaque eveniet ipsum ducimus odio quae natus vero magnam, similique amet ea a eius veritatis? Rerum, voluptas quos illo animi impedit voluptate illum tenetur dolor quis nam doloribus, a nobis, mollitia ullam modi sit quo nostrum autem ipsum. Inventore, illum. Unde, facilis in molestias eligendi corporis ratione quia facere voluptatem aperiam esse ducimus praesentium minus iste doloribus temporibus possimus beatae optio quasi maiores, incidunt, eveniet doloremque modi. Veritatis at ducimus ab autem reiciendis, non et assumenda dicta quia repudiandae, aspernatur deleniti dignissimos placeat ea a iure dolore dolorem porro velit, accusamus corporis recusandae amet totam? Vel nostrum tenetur numquam nemo quo ab soluta tempora, culpa facere. Et nam ipsum sint atque ad dolor. Nam, minus quos facilis rem et repudiandae ducimus sint!

            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} >

    </Container>
  )
}

export default OurStory
